the cottage this is one of danielle steel 's best books . it is about cooper winslow , a fading movie actor and lady 's man who is in financial trouble . she develops the character of `` coop '' well so it is easy to visualize him . coop decides to rent out his `` cottage '' guest wings for $ 10,000 a month to two different tenants . the story centers around his new tenants , their romances , activities and children . in the end , coop learns valuable lessons about sacrifice , giving to others and true love . a interesting story with a good message